.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b200b2a30802993d908d96ad5a6d43dafaecbb6a","tid":270283,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>裝修後=垃圾</blockquote><br />\n佢個仔1接手就要立下馬威嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ccb6744be71722a4184ac61c019d6ef53c0b2af","tid":270283,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:57:26.000Z","msg":"細份又貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a2845c6c6083e29785cebad76277ed011d631f","tid":270283,"uid":59544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T19:04:06.000Z","msg":"唔係唔好食 但好普通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔明點解啲人要煲永年<br />\n啲野又細份 變相覺得貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2241e168ccdf7a1ae3ba0b9c148be4d1b799e9","tid":270283,"uid":9778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T19:18:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>元朗人表示永年係垃圾，元朗啲好味野永遠唔會係出名果堆，包括b仔</blockquote><br />\n果間乜嫂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n田中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以上講既都係出名但元朗人覺得難食</blockquote><br />\n晚晚去食個班都係街外人？<br />\n咪又係你班元朗傻鳩最多<br />\n你估個個得閒入你大西北食碗車仔面？<br />\n唔知點解永遠永年/b仔post都總有班撚樣跳出黎話去食既都唔係元朗人<br />\n好撚清高咁"},{"pid":"bf0431aeeed583178db14421e6f271bbcb6e5eb9","tid":270283,"uid":38867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T19:32:14.000Z","msg":"想問下元朗人有邊間車仔推介？"},{"pid":"1992ecd1da2acf0289266dbe789ed4393bcc8d70","tid":270283,"uid":10531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T19:33:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>元朗仲有無其他車仔麵介紹</blockquote><br />\n炮杖坊果間 唔記得叫咩名"},{"pid":"42986d443b45d639010671f315c6aa41803e391e","tid":270283,"uid":29434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T19:51:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>元朗仲有無其他車仔麵介紹</blockquote><br />\n炮杖坊果間 唔記得叫咩名</blockquote><br />\n炮杖坊那間叫 榮記，佢既粉仔真係稱霸<br />\n<br />\n當你食過港九新新界既車仔麵，你就會明白永年真係屈機，辣汁無得輸"},{"pid":"11851dfb09d37201947f42b2a8e55c82075bdb91","tid":270283,"uid":21164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T20:06:40.000Z","msg":"朗屏宵夜檔間車仔麵，抵食+好味"},{"pid":"0196cfa747b8b19aa5ef93faf3ec3ec5418112e3","tid":270283,"uid":73421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T20:10:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朗屏宵夜檔間車仔麵，抵食+好味</blockquote><br />\n識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8d5d2b878f1d4de7bec40ef77be168b60f60c2","tid":270283,"uid":27019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T20:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f2b36bd969934f421cfe848acfb4887dc024b8","tid":270283,"uid":21164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T20:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>朗屏宵夜檔間車仔麵，抵食+好味</blockquote><br />\n識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n由細食到大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要嗌魚肉餸 恥笑班排長龍買生菜魚肉嘅7頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ad54dd64905fe1140bdf2c9285fa125e86fd9c","tid":270283,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T20:19:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>元朗人表示永年係垃圾，元朗啲好味野永遠唔會係出名果堆，包括b仔</blockquote><br />\n果間乜嫂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n田中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以上講既都係出名但元朗人覺得難食</blockquote><br />\n晚晚去食個班都係街外人？<br />\n咪又係你班元朗傻鳩最多<br />\n你估個個得閒入你大西北食碗車仔面？<br />\n唔知點解永遠永年/b仔post都總有班撚樣跳出黎話去食既都唔係元朗人<br />\n好撚清高咁</blockquote><br />\n永年1半1半<br /